Implement functionality to:
Add/view/update/delete tasks.
Track habit streaks.
Take quick notes.
Save/load user session.
Log every action.

productivity_tracker/
├── streamlit_app.py                 # Main Streamlit UI file
├── utils/
│   ├── tasks.py                     # Task management logic
│   ├── habits.py                    # Habit tracking logic
│   └── notes.py                     # Notes handling logic
├── data/
│   ├── tasks.csv                    # Task data (CSV)
│   ├── habits.json                  # Habit data (JSON)
│   ├── notes.txt                    # Notes (TXT)
│   ├── session.pkl                  # Session state (Pickle)
│   └── activity.log                 # Activity logs
└── README.md                        # Project overview
